{"tid":505291,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"油塘路試","createTime":"2017-12-21T03:19:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-02T09:12:53.000Z","uid":129708,"like":2,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"b42080bb54bae283ea6badc03510ea59253ca405","tid":505291,"uid":129708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T03:19:35.000Z","msg":"聽日就考油塘 今日學最後一堂雖然無俾師傅罵甘多 但都係有罵幾句 但其實都真系好驚 始終好驚有啲位做得吾好 各位巴打們可唔可以比少少心得我 邊個位需要注意多啲 因為我自己覺得啲位驚自己注意唔到，有心既巴打們比少少少貼士細路，等我留意下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58e434f06a82404e99411416a499d59885732397","tid":505291,"uid":20570,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T04:11:40.000Z","msg":"放鬆啲個人 我考車個日上最後一堂都比師父屌我判斷力唔夠 到考既時候就睇清楚路面既情況 有啲位做果斷啲 唔好驚就得 最後pass咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：3take 油塘"},{"pid":"db54591679e9e5fd664250222c2a3428893f6693","tid":505291,"uid":145972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T04:15:06.000Z","msg":"1線係多死車慢慢黎就得多望鏡<br />\n<br />\n利申油塘2take pass"},{"pid":"b7f906d7c400658ad170504b73162b42979fe7bb","tid":505291,"uid":53798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T04:16:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1線係多死車慢慢黎就得多望鏡<br />\n<br />\n利申油塘2take pass</blockquote><br />\n仁宇圍 2 take pass"},{"pid":"c7b65bfda2a82290dd41957dc97e933928b1e08e","tid":505291,"uid":72979,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T04:17:32.000Z","msg":"做足師傅俾你提示<br />\n確保要無車先好出車行<br />\n檸頭望鏡大動作少少都唔怕<br />\n緊張就少不免 祝君好運<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72df2bd63c8ef8f068bdded4e5dc989863b7bd65","tid":505291,"uid":322,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T04:21:59.000Z","msg":"油塘1take<br />\n跟李師傅學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97afb39cbc08548e5b3333e9df31ba006b2a6dde","tid":505291,"uid":322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T04:23:45.000Z","msg":"最緊要 打燈 望鏡 轉頭"},{"pid":"81ddc7bce6477eecfe7632e30b74edbd76cecc29","tid":505291,"uid":57488,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T04:25:11.000Z","msg":"幾點，落嚟同你打氣"},{"pid":"872198d883181d9a0d54ba09835c05ac19d32948","tid":505291,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T04:27:36.000Z","msg":"做動作要講出聲比呀sir知"},{"pid":"4e6be5d06435a923960ed35d55aa70e64249082a","tid":505291,"uid":62192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T04:28:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聽日就考油塘 今日學最後一堂雖然無俾師傅罵甘多 但都係有罵幾句 但其實都真系好驚 始終好驚有啲位做得<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">吾</span>好 各位巴打們可唔可以比少少心得我 邊個位需要注意多啲 因為我自己覺得啲位驚自己注意唔到，有心既巴打們比少少少貼士細路，等我留意下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"081fa076b5eae24bb62383df4aaf627cdabf129a","tid":505291,"uid":114976,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T04:32:40.000Z","msg":"甘 吾<br />\n炒撚硬啦"},{"pid":"aaa26f2f2fbcadd47508470dccbe60bea280f729","tid":505291,"uid":11560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T04:35:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>油塘1take<br />\n跟李師傅學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我都係李師傅，係咪長毛，成日著波衫果個？<br />\n<br />\n出迴旋處轉左入試場前小心有紅van cut入嚟，同埋大本型商場對出入迴旋處前既馬路，小心有廢老沖出嚟。<br />\n<br />\n記得停車熄鑰入一波<br />\n<br />\nBTW 你棍定自動波？<br />\n<br />\n1take pass棍van<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"995b87cafc080b0d86f87c4fb082826485193af3","tid":505291,"uid":127046,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T04:36:29.000Z","msg":"俾啲信心..最緊要係望鏡望鏡望鏡!開車前左前右後鏡都要望足!動作要好大!我就係係油塘fail左就係爭無望足!其實油塘好易揸..同埋你出迴旋處記得記得記得要睇清楚..迴旋處轉左個條線多數有小巴上落車..小人咪等下多人就cut線出但記得望有無車先!其他無咩特別!希望你1 take pass!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"500a645846ca262ecf497c1da560a6c014e2b4c3","tid":505291,"uid":13157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T04:55:19.000Z","msg":"今晚有冇時間啊？ 今晚想出一出去啓德碼頭<br />\n去之前可以帶你行下 我住藍田<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我亦都係考油塘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49dff2591afc6946a2614788de927fc22df749a0","tid":505291,"uid":35365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T05:01:02.000Z","msg":"聽日咩時間考<br />\n上晝既話多數鯉魚門下面大車塞死<br />\n考官多數會玩2線<br />\n2線就冇乜難度 主要係小心迴旋處同埋最尾入返嘉榮街d廢老亂過馬路<br />\n<br />\n利申油塘1take"},{"pid":"5b501a0e68c91bfc113746d248a0d49754af5aa7","tid":505291,"uid":129708,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T11:33:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>放鬆啲個人 我考車個日上最後一堂都比師父屌我判斷力唔夠 到考既時候就睇清楚路面既情況 有啲位做果斷啲 唔好驚就得 最後pass咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：3take 油塘</blockquote><br />\n多謝你巴打 我學個陣最驚都系過燈 成日驚佢轉紅燈 吾敢果斷過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我會努力"},{"pid":"f879aeaf4681ebad57b09c19748524824f86f8ae","tid":505291,"uid":129708,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T11:35:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>油塘1take<br />\n跟李師傅學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我都係李師傅，係咪長毛，成日著波衫果個？<br />\n<br />\n出迴旋處轉左入試場前小心有紅van cut入嚟，同埋大本型商場對出入迴旋處前既馬路，小心有廢老沖出嚟。<br />\n<br />\n記得停車熄鑰入一波<br />\n<br />\nBTW 你棍定自動波？<br />\n<br />\n1take pass棍van<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我棍波阿 我都開得好小心 因為真係太多老人家同埋後面啲車 好似趕住投胎甘 成日催 多謝巴打提醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b99ceee41779e70f5e265105f89ad2503890e201","tid":505291,"uid":129708,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T11:37:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>俾啲信心..最緊要係望鏡望鏡望鏡!開車前左前右後鏡都要望足!動作要好大!我就係係油塘fail左就係爭無望足!其實油塘好易揸..同埋你出迴旋處記得記得記得要睇清楚..迴旋處轉左個條線多數有小巴上落車..小人咪等下多人就cut線出但記得望有無車先!其他無咩特別!希望你1 take pass!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多謝巴打 我都諗住過親車都望架啦 因為做多好過做少 唔會蝕底 ，我都希望可以順利1take pass 我會努力💪🏻"},{"pid":"4ec8a9072536d0607b38b9ec580c6f55ffc76d92","tid":505291,"uid":15237,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T11:40:41.000Z","msg":"吾你老母呀 祝你永世都唔pass"},{"pid":"43b1607af6b9265fc88a7677ca52e5c5d4ca399a","tid":505291,"uid":129708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T11:43:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今晚有冇時間啊？ 今晚想出一出去啓德碼頭<br />\n去之前可以帶你行下 我住藍田<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我亦都係考油塘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為我太驚 所以報多堂 今晚學 想再練熟少少 <br />\n多謝你阿巴打 因為我學完就返去休息下 養足精神 <br />\n多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"909825384e38298e02439f18866b8350bf0e682e","tid":505291,"uid":129708,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T11:44:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>吾你老母呀 祝你永世都唔pass</blockquote><br />\n哈哈 唔好意思 不過你入黎都係當支持我架啦 多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74e83511a70941b64377084bd34ecee560dfeae6","tid":505291,"uid":129708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T11:46:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1線係多死車慢慢黎就得多望鏡<br />\n<br />\n利申油塘2take pass</blockquote><br />\n多謝你巴打 我聽師傅講 多數考2/3線多 希望真係 哈哈 我會留意多啲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"474ebb566105fa0b87518a362b2333b26a3cf2cc","tid":505291,"uid":129708,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T11:48:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做足師傅俾你提示<br />\n確保要無車先好出車行<br />\n檸頭望鏡大動作少少都唔怕<br />\n緊張就少不免 祝君好運<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都好想當佢係平時師傅甘樣考 希望做到最好表現就好似練車咁樣 我都打算誇張所有動作 同埋做親都出下聲 希望咁樣有用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99cfcd3da387a9f4859ed98c5fdba8cbdd110eb4","tid":505291,"uid":129708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T11:48:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做動作要講出聲比呀sir知</blockquote><br />\n知道 多謝巴打 好有愛大家 謝謝你們<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9447c25c1715d2489c55af61828df1b0316c894c","tid":505291,"uid":49,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T11:55:06.000Z","msg":"迴旋處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n臨返考場左轉個到街市位好多盲毛"},{"pid":"ee74c436275e8a4b0f032b248a418cf3f14cdf5c","tid":505291,"uid":49,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T11:55:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>迴旋處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n臨返考場左轉個到街市位好多盲毛</blockquote><br />\n我就係衰街口有條撚頭衝出黎  一齊踩肥左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a865cc736b9f1211dc87a6a16d4c42df52d84044","tid":505291,"uid":129708,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T11:58:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>迴旋處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n臨返考場左轉個到街市位好多盲毛</blockquote><br />\n我就係衰街口有條撚頭衝出黎  一齊踩肥左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都知道呢個位真系好危 我打算兩波轉灣個陣轉番一波 其實甘樣做會吾會話唔恰當？"},{"pid":"a59ba2fa9b621dc22b74ac56c02622ca0dbb26fd","tid":505291,"uid":129708,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T11:58:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>迴旋處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n臨返考場左轉個到街市位好多盲毛</blockquote><br />\n我就係衰街口有條撚頭衝出黎  一齊踩肥左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都知道呢個位真系好危 我打算兩波轉灣個陣轉番一波 其實甘樣做會吾會話唔恰當？</blockquote><br />\n 唔 sorry <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c59d0fd67f13442d875a4d13c24a7402bc8db3f2","tid":505291,"uid":65939,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T11:58:45.000Z","msg":"最緊要天時地利人和！<br />\n<br />\n天時：無落雨無交通意外<br />\n地利：放哂聖誕假條街無乜車無乜死車，最好朝早考仲少<br />\n人和：條街無人，無19呀伯衝出黎，考官夠9hea，仲要唔好衰自己on9野<br />\n<br />\n所以運氣係佔好多<br />\n<br />\n利申：兩年前差唔多時間油塘1take pass"},{"pid":"6511640eef72eaa1828e877debadd86350147fb4","tid":505291,"uid":129708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T11:58:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>[quote]迴旋處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n臨返考場左轉個到街市位好多盲毛</blockquote><br />\n我就係衰街口有條撚頭衝出黎  一齊踩肥左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都知道呢個位真係好危 我打算兩波轉灣個陣轉番一波 其實甘樣做會唔會話唔恰當？</blockquote>"},{"pid":"61216de45aa3631773e8fda181cb41fb3e38bf3e","tid":505291,"uid":129708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T12:00:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最緊要天時地利人和！<br />\n<br />\n天時：無落雨無交通意外<br />\n地利：放哂聖誕假條街無乜車無乜死車，最好朝早考仲少<br />\n人和：條街無人，無19呀伯衝出黎，考官夠9hea，仲要唔好衰自己on9野<br />\n<br />\n所以運氣係佔好多<br />\n<br />\n利申：兩年前差唔多時間油塘1take pass</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我運氣一向都唔係好好運 所以唯有技術方面做好啲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  多謝巴打"},{"pid":"b864e4caad4014dd235cb97c7d8f2e237f00218f","tid":505291,"uid":129708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T12:15:11.000Z","msg":"想問下呢 其實三波係咪得1線上斜路前同埋 2線直路有機會先轉 其他路用番二波想穩陣啲 得唔得架？"},{"pid":"fcc41291e6f40371b33017aa608ee938eda02006","tid":505291,"uid":11560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T12:37:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問下呢 其實三波係咪得1線上斜路前同埋 2線直路有機會先轉 其他路用番二波想穩陣啲 得唔得架？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n記得師傅講過係俾考官睇下你識唔識入三波"},{"pid":"7903c05e405843a8f986b2ac1a2844641d448ba8","tid":505291,"uid":2212,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T12:55:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>迴旋處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n臨返考場左轉個到街市位好多盲毛</blockquote><br />\n我就係衰街口有條撚頭衝出黎  一齊踩肥左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都知道呢個位真系好危 我打算兩波轉灣個陣轉番一波 其實甘樣做會吾會話唔恰當？</blockquote><br />\n未必夠時間...<br />\n<br />\n過咗迴旋處行左線其實要睇住右邊有無車cut 過黎，去到彎位已經要偷位挨右(記得打燈!)，轉入去個時師傅教踩定一半極力子驚有人衝出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4a48615dbe74c9d5e816cb381a2d3ef7d46ff33","tid":505291,"uid":9080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T13:40:18.000Z","msg":"加油巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11c3aa3ef1e6e38bbba710280f1cab5835962294","tid":505291,"uid":141846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB