src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f08f91873f8b00200bb70ebe4ec28421b52767ac","tid":505291,"uid":141846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7dac786df5c6972911cf5619cd65c25df4225b19","tid":505291,"uid":75256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T01:29:33.000Z","msg":"心事重重巴打考成點？見你咁耐都未蒲頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T05:08:28.000Z","msg":"炒車死撚左"},{"pid":"be0dd9627c3c163d09ad2fa9b06a6e136bfce98c","tid":505291,"uid":30895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b501a0e68c91bfc113746d248a0d49754af5aa7","tid":505291,"uid":129708,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T11:33:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>放鬆啲個人 我考車個日上最後一堂都比師父屌我判斷力唔夠 到考既時候就睇清楚路面既情況 有啲位做果斷啲 唔好驚就得 最後pass咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：3take 油塘</blockquote><br />\n多謝你巴打 我學個陣最驚都系過燈 成日驚佢轉紅燈 吾敢果斷過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我會努力"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T05:21:46.000Z","msg":"轉紅燈咪收油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ccb6c036f5397fe31b6e4737244d47ae6b63bb8","tid":505291,"uid":100697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T09:52:16.000Z","msg":"今日油塘考2線 passed<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e569403e2031f241bf349cc32972a4264245edef","tid":505291,"uid":11332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T02:51:03.000Z","msg":"3月22考油塘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 緊張 而家師傅同我練緊果兩條線 有時話我唔敢踩油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44b0719fa8439f655437a8aa815721c5213cbcc0","tid":505291,"uid":166588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0901441c5e500a21de2b86ba3983a1b187d13a14","tid":505291,"uid":127046,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d1304a242f20ccebf14cc723606ef0558b4afb95","tid":505291,"uid":101168,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T11:09:50.000Z","msg":"我都1月考油塘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  其實都有啲肯定肥佬，但都想問大家 出迴旋處前係咪一定要停車？ 同埋我靠右出迴旋處，要第二個路口轉入，出個時要路要打燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBTW 聽日考個位巴打 加油呀！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T05:52:26.000Z","msg":"無理由你見到前面迴旋處無車你都停<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T04:13:20.000Z","msg":"考試既話就停左先好啲，其實迴旋處唔係真係咁難，最緊要無車先出，唔好入錯線<br />\n<br />\n利申：油塘考左兩次，第二次Pass"},{"pid":"7e3ff6e8ef0670ea1d0f10119d2c4b54857ecee9","tid":505291,"uid":76135,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T04:22:28.000Z","msg":"油塘第一個路口好睇運氣. 望左邊時眼尾望埋考牌官."},{"pid":"b1180729bbbdceee0220c1975911562bb374ab0e","tid":505291,"uid":100760,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7e3ff6e8ef0670ea1d0f10119d2c4b54857ecee9","tid":505291,"uid":76135,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T04:22:28.000Z","msg":"油塘第一個路口好睇運氣. 望左邊時眼尾望埋考牌官."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T11:48:20.000Z","msg":"係好撚講運氣，根本望唔到有冇車嚟，琴日考，見冇車就出，點知原來有車，好彩係架好慢嘅學車，同埋都有啲距離，最後好彩合格"},{"pid":"4d746c11cc444d5c4f9eb4eb1ffcf34e7b4c3bdd","tid":505291,"uid":100760,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"9447c25c1715d2489c55af61828df1b0316c894c","tid":505291,"uid":49,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T11:55:06.000Z","msg":"迴旋處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n臨返考場左轉個到街市位好多盲毛"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T12:00:31.000Z","msg":"呢個位師傅多次強調預咗要慢同停車讓行人，考試時我就停比佢地過<br />\n去到前少少接近運輸署門口，有個阿嬸推住個坐輪椅嘅阿婆，喺車路想推上行人路，我停車等佢，點知推左幾次都推唔撚到上去，最後個阿嬸喺車路右邊示意叫我繼續揸<br />\n我老閪都唔撚郁，最後佢縮返去左邊啲死車隔籬我先開車，心諗呢個阿嬸係咪運輸署派嘅演員嚟伏鳩人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}